```r
updateId <- function(df, feature){
  newIDs <- c()
  for (rID in df[[feature]]){
    nID <- players_raw[[which(players_raw$retroID == rID),"playerID"]]
    newIDs <- c(newIDs, nID)
  }
  df[[feature]] <- newIDs
  df
}
```
